{"tid":1283716,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行管會周四開會商立會損毀情況 更新：2019/07/03 23:06","createTime":"2019-07-04T01:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T02:01:25.000Z","uid":27717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"71583cf583b8bc74a163bf9aaad5b9de961b1da9","tid":1283716,"uid":27717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:38:57.000Z","msg":"今日行會又開會<br />\n<br />\nsource:有線<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/551915/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E8%A1%8C%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%83%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E9%96%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%95%86%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%90%8D%E6%AF%80%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F551915%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%259B%259B%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2595%2586%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2590%258D%25E6%25AF%2580%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B3%2581&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O2bkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=562b2860\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F551915%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%259B%259B%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2595%2586%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2590%258D%25E6%25AF%2580%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B3%2581&h=57330d3e\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/551915/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E8%A1%8C%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%83%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E9%96%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%95%86%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%90%8D%E6%AF%80%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81</a><br />\n<br />\n七月一日大型示威活動之後，政部總部重開，立法會仍然關閉，傳媒獲安排拍攝入面的情況。行管會明天在<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">金鐘政府合署</span></span>召開特別會議，商討損毀情況，警方晚上完成搜證。 <br />\n<br />\n警員在立法會示威區檢查示威者留下的雜物，分類展示，有鐵枝，有磚頭，有不同質料的盾牌，也有壓縮氣體罐。大樓玻璃幕牆全碎了，工人用木板封好。立法會安排傳媒下午入大樓看裡面的情況，四周都被塗鴉，鐵馬陣未清走。走廊的閉路電視被人扯下來，平時議員見記者的咪架只餘下幾支咪，新聞發布室整個音響控制台被拉出來。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n臨入會議廳，歷任主席的肖像剩下黃宏發及施偉賢的兩幅仍掛在牆上。會議廳一片凌亂，滿地是示威者物資，還有食物。地下一層，圖書館門口撞毀，前面豎立了一塊牌，叫人「保護圖書」，對出的展品櫃亦有告示寫著「不可破壞」。立法會行管會星期四早上會實地視察損毀情況，十時半移師金鐘政府合署舉行特別會議。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方就在 Facebook 發布在大樓內搜證的相片，在會議廳內掃指紋、拍照記錄，拔走示威者的貼紙，有組織罪案及三合會調查科、鑑證科及政府化驗所人員都有參與。警方指會做 DNA 鑑證及激光掃描，必定會跟進到底，將犯事的人繩之於法。"},{"pid":"b671c94fb158a4ec59e65e1683e12450418969b4","tid":1283716,"uid":268410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:54:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩女警疑於社交平台煽動他人犯罪<br />\n<a href=\"http://mango01.club/view3/4799\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmango01.club%2Fview3%2F4799&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O2bkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=bac958c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://mango01.club/view3/4799</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ATXR1Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ATXR1Q.png&h=9ec67d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李力持教唆示威者圍中聯辦禮賓府 被Cap圖知衰急刪帖<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190703/59785001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190703%2F59785001&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O2bkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=9324e28b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190703%2F59785001&h=17b3b172\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190703/59785001</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PDq7uOK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPDq7uOK.png&h=a91e43d3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5724709b4a5faa1f9eddc3f271ad3fffa9e56c41","tid":1283716,"uid":169116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:01:25.000Z","msg":"金鐘政府合署仲有律政司刑事檢控科"}]}